title: Shaolin - PS1
description:
Hello all, it took me FOREVER to find this on the web, as far as I know there is no working and active torrent, but I managed to find it through a certain other site that is a pain to use, so I decided to make life a little easier for anyone searching for this.

This is in fact the old PS1 Shaolin game, released in EU and UK if memory serves. I've tested it extensively with ePSXe 1.7.0 and it works perfectly for me, so have fun with this old, hard-to-find game!
